<P>__{(grins)}
<D>__{often enough to keep the franchise.}
<C>__{margo}
<D>__{a foursquare, upright, downright, forthright married lady... that's for me. and no more make believe! off stage or on... remember, lloyd.}
<P>__{(lloyd nods)}
<D>__{i mean it, now. grown up women only, i might even play a mother only one child, of course, not over eight...}
<P>__{(they all smile)}
