<P>__{(explodes)}
<D>__{what?}
<A>__{margo misinterprets her vehemence.}
<C>__{margo}
<P>__{(hastily)}
<D>__{now wait a minute, you're always so touchy about his plays, it isn't the part it's a great part. and a fine play. but not for me anymore not a foursquare, upright, downright, forthright married lady.}
<C>__{lloyd}
<D>__{what's your being married got to do with it?}
