<D>__{it means i've finally got a life to live! i don't have to play parts i'm too old for just because i've got nothing to do with my nights!}
<P>__{(then quietly)}
<D>__{i know you've made plans. i will make it up to you, believe me. i will tour a year with this one, anything only you do understand don't you, lloyd?}
